{"tid":746050,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HTC執柒咗佢啦你！！！","createTime":"2018-07-17T09:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T04:05:28.000Z","uid":105894,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"32435814c212fd50891710cb1f568ed10ede6a45","tid":746050,"uid":105894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"本身都對htc好有好感 用過m8同10仔 但最近發生呢d嘢令我覺得呢間公司冇得救<br />\n1）facebook page inbox問嘢一個星期後先答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）部10仔用咗一年舊電已經打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3）拎去維修中心整左成個月先有得拎 仲要冇人通知有得拎 要自己打上去客戶服務跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4）終於有得拎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知到sim card detect唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （整之前係正常嘅）<br />\n5）又試拎過去整 師傅話驗到前鏡頭有黑點（整之前無異常）反而張sim card驗唔到有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小結：QC垃圾 公司就執冇錢 冇人手做客服+售後支援維修 搞到要外判維修 垃圾聯強借故鑿水 <br />\nConclusion: 愛惜生命 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿買HTC！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"84e2dd37f57e67919780def73d5bf4ed0bcf3fbe","tid":746050,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲都垃圾嚟 早兩年買過部HTC 用咗半年已經頂唔順要換iphone"},{"pid":"317da78e3d3be18ab4ff2d520f4fed9d6179eaa2","tid":746050,"uid":164092,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:19:51.000Z","msg":"Sony同HTC都係垃圾"},{"pid":"c0ed5d4a76416bc243e53d4488b4b67695ec3f29","tid":746050,"uid":181905,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"屌拿媽,有apple唔買係要買D垃圾,自己拎黎賤"},{"pid":"a64b655f96f603f675937b4b36e2f2c1bd12104e","tid":746050,"uid":164092,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c0ed5d4a76416bc243e53d4488b4b67695ec3f29","tid":746050,"uid":181905,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201